1
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:48,440
Here.

2
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:50,120
If we find your wallet,

3
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,900
we'll let you know right away.

4
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:52,560
Okay.

5
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,520
All right, go on home now.

6
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,200
From now on, don't go wandering around

7
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,280
in the middle of the night for no reason.

8
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:57,680
Thank you.

9
00:00:57,680 --> 00:00:58,720
Okay. Off you go.

10
00:01:06,440 --> 00:01:07,880
This is my entire life savings that I scrimped and saved

11
00:01:07,880 --> 00:01:10,000
without my girlfriend knowing.

12
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:12,120
This is as much as I can help you, bro.

13
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:13,480
If you're touched, finish your business

14
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:15,400
and come back to write songs immediately.

15
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,440
That stuff written by AI

16
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:17,500
really has no soul.

17
00:01:19,039 --> 00:01:19,800
Mr. Liu Ma.

18
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,680
Do you know that between people,

19
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:23,120
there is a magnetic repulsion effect?

20
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:23,920
No repulsion.

21
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,800
I have something to tell you.

22
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,360
I thought about it all night.

23
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:30,200
The person you're looking for probably isn't Yanwang.

24
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,880
That character has multiple pronunciations.

25
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:33,410
Here, we pronounce it "Ai".

26
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,039
Aiwang?

27
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,680
Yes, that's the character.

28
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,320
But...

29
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,360
But what?

30
00:01:46,479 --> 00:01:48,000
People named Yanwang here

31
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,520
are as common as Zhang Wei.

32
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:54,100
How long is this going to take?

33
00:01:57,479 --> 00:01:59,539
Brother, have some breakfast first.

34
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,400
Ma'am,

35
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:02,810
two bowls of rice noodles, please.

36
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:05,520
Let's tell our nephew

37
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,050
that we're safe.

38
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:08,880
Ma'er.

39
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:10,280
It's Uncle.

40
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,460
Your Little Uncle,

41
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,840
I found him for you.

42
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,600
Where is the money I asked for?

43
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:16,160
I...

44
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:20,320
Brother.

45
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,800
That was too rude.

46
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,360
Hurry up and transfer the money to me.

47
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,200
Or else, his pinky

48
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:29,880
won't be safe.

49
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:31,210
Are you watching a skit?

50
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,360
Chopping off a finger.

51
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,320
That's such a cliché.

52
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,240
My grandpa wouldn't even watch this stuff.

53
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,200
The acting is terrible, too.

54
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:39,520
I could act better than that.

55
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,200
Liu Ma,

56
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:42,400
you actually dared to bring backup?

57
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,040
He's not backup.

58
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:43,720
He isn't. He's just...

59
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:45,480
Playing gangster in a society ruled by law?

60
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:46,940
Brother, call the police!

61
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,520
We agreed on ten days.

62
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:52,800
I'll transfer you 5,000 first. Let my uncle go.

63
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,360
Fine.

64
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:54,690
I'll be waiting.

65
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,640
Did you get scammed?

66
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,370
Stop worrying about it.

67
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,490
The rice noodles are ready.

68
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:06,400
Coming.

69
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:17,960
Here.

70
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:21,360
This is a Lincang breakfast specialty.

71
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:22,360
Eat up.

72
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,740
I understand how you feel.

73
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:29,500
But you can't search on an empty stomach.

74
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:44,079
Can you really find Yanwang?

75
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:53,700
How about this?

76
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,960
If you help me find Yanwang,

77
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,620
I'll transfer you 5,000 yuan.

78
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,440
Bro, I don't want your money.

79
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:02,370
There's something I want to talk to you about.

80
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,160
Look.

81
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:06,940
Lincang is hosting a band competition soon.

82
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,570
What are you getting at?

83
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,210
You're highly skilled,

84
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,920
and I have a decent sense of music.

85
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,000
I can play rhythm for you.

86
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,000
Let's form a band together.

87
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:17,930
Not interested.

88
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,690
But the prize money is 100,000.

89
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:23,840
That's just a trap set by capital

90
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:26,360
to fool young kids like you.

91
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:27,560
No.

92
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,240
If we team up, we'll definitely win.

93
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,300
We'll be big stars.

94
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:33,440
What makes you think you can win?

95
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:35,000
And what makes you think

96
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,800
winning will make you a big star?

97
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,920
I have you.

98
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:40,370
I just want to start a band with you.

99
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,000
I want to be someone like you.

100
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,120
Be like me?

101
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:44,640
You can see for yourself.

102
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:45,640
Right now, I'm just a

103
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:47,360
loser up to his eyeballs in debt.

104
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,240
I came to Lincang this time,

105
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,600
and if I don't bring back the money,

106
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,530
my uncle is dead.

107
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,170
I might end up dead, too.

108
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,240
If you've got too much time on your hands,

109
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,280
go get a job.

110
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,220
Don't mess around with music.

111
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:01,040
But music is my dream.

112
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,640
I don't have time to play house with a kid,

113
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:06,360
chasing after dreams.

114
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,290
Understood.

115
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:23,760
Um...

116
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:25,920
Excuse me.

117
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:44,840
Get in.

118
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,880
Why are you following me?

119
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,409
We're looking for Yanwang.

120
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,160
These are all the people nearby

121
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,160
named Yanwang.

122
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,240
No.

123
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:36,920
Excuse me.

124
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:38,970
Is Yanwang here?

125
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:39,840
Hang on.

126
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:42,000
Bro, someone's here for you.

127
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,280
Can I help you two?

128
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,000
Never mind.

129
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:51,010
Sorry to bother you.

130
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,090
Is Yanwang home?

131
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,320
Yanwang,

132
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,120
someone's here for you.

133
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:26,960
Thank you, Grandma.

134
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,800
I'll take you there.

135
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:36,960
Mr. Liu Ma.

136
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,520
Stop following me.

137
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:40,920
Get in the car.

138
00:07:44,159 --> 00:07:45,490
Slow down. Don't hit me.

139
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,360
Mr. Liu Ma.

140
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,490
Thanks, Auntie.

141
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,680
Come, try this.

142
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,200
These are Lincang specialties.

143
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:00,960
They're delicious.

144
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:01,600
Thank you.

145
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:05,680
Here.

146
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,280
What is this?

147
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,930
Fried bamboo worms.

148
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:13,480
It's full of collagen and very nutritious.

149
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:31,960
Take it away.

150
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,200
Can you take these away?

151
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,039
Teacher Liu Ma.

152
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:35,039
Just have a taste.

153
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:37,299
Don't call me Teacher.

154
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,679
Then I'll call you Brother.

155
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,320
Whatever.

156
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:42,720
Brother, I have a good idea.

157
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,890
I won't form a band with you.

158
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:46,240
Worst case scenario,

159
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,680
even if we don't get the prize money,

160
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:49,400
we can just shout it out on stage.

161
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,560
There are so many people there.

162
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:51,620
Word spreads fast.

163
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:52,680
Won't that work?

164
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,440
The money in your pocket

165
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,760
is barely enough for one night at a hostel.

166
00:08:57,760 --> 00:08:58,690
Starting today,

167
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:00,000
your meals, lodging,

168
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,800
and finding people are all on me.

169
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:05,600
Fine. I won't say any more.

170
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:11,880
Bro.

171
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,660
AI really can write songs.

172
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,960
AI can do plenty of things.

173
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:21,240
Generate an image for me.

174
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:23,340
Halfway up a tea mountain,

175
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:25,780
a house with green tiles and white walls.

176
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:33,880
This...

177
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:35,960
Recognize it?

178
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,160
Isn't it right over there?
